Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • Message
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    public class Message
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class represents a Message object. Message objects have a string content, username of the sender, and a username of the recipient.
